#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today we are learning about giving our children praise. \n"
"\n"
"Praise helps build a positive relationship and encourages good behaviour!\n"
"\n"
"Let‚Äôs first reflect on our own experience with praise."
msgstr ""
"Namhlanje sifunda ngokunika abantwana bethu izincomo. \n"
"\n"
"Ukuncoma kunceda ukwakha ubudlelwane obuhle kwaye kukhuthaza nesimilo esilungileyo!\n"
"\n"
"Masiqale sicacise ngamava ethu ngokuncoma."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Think about the last time someone thanked you, or said you did something great."
msgstr "Cinga malunga nexesha lokugqibela apho uye wabulelwa ngomnye umntu, okanye wakuxelela ukuba wenze into entle kakhulu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How did it make you feel?"
msgstr "Yakwenza waziva njani?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Proud"
msgstr "Benebhongo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel proud."
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Ukunconywa rhoqo kusenza sizive sinebhongo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Uyavuya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel happy!"
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Ukunconywa rhoqo kusenza sizive sonwabile!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Embarrassed"
msgstr "Ndineentloni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sometimes being praised makes us feel embarrassed, usually because we are not used to it. Remember, everybody deserves praise!"
msgstr "Ngamanye amaxesha ukunconywa kusenza sizive sineentloni, ngokwesiqhelo ngenxa yokuba asiyiqhelanga lento. Khumbula, wonke umntu ufanelwe kukunconywa!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"We all feel better when we are praised.\n"
"\n"
"Praising your child when they behave well will make them want to behave that way more often. \n"
"\n"
"It also creates a positive and loving relationship between you."
msgstr ""
"Sonke siziva ngcono xa sinconywa.\n"
"\n"
"Ukuncoma umntwana wakho xa eziphethe kakuhle kuya kumenza afune ukuziphatha ngolo hlobo rhoqo. \n"
"\n"
"Yakha ubudlelwane obuhle kunye nobunothando phakathi kwakho."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how praise can help you and your family"
msgstr "Cofa udlala umamele ukuba ukuncoma kungakunceda njani wena kunye nosapho lwakho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"When was the last time you were praised? Can you praise yourself for something right now? Praise makes us all feel good. \n"
"\n"
"It is good to praise our children when they have done well, because when we do that, they will do more of that good behaviour we want to see.\n"
"\n"
"And let's remember to praise ourselves too, for big or small things!"
msgstr ""
"Molweni, nonke.\n"
"\n"
"Kwakunini ukugqibela kwakho ukunconywa? Uyakwazi ukuzincoma ngento ngoku? Ukuncoma kusenza sizive sonke sonwabile. \n"
"\n"
"Kuhle ukuncoma abantwana bethu xa benze kakuhle, kuba xa sisenza loo nto, bazakusenza ngakumbi esasimilo silungileyo sifuna ukusibona.\n"
"\n"
"Kwaye masikhumbule ukuzincoma nathi, ngezinto ezinkulu okanye ezincinci!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs look at how @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises her son, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, during one-on-one time."
msgstr "Masibone ukuba uncome njani u@data.characters.f3_mother.name unyana wakhe u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name,ngelixa lomnye nomnye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You found one striped sock and one with dots. Let‚Äôs find socks that match."
msgstr "Ufumene ikawusi enemigca enye kwaye enye inamachokoza. Masifumane iikawusi ezihambelanayo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Another sock! This one is white. It‚Äôs frustrating to try to find a matching pair when there are so many clothes to look through."
msgstr "Enye ikawusi! lena imhlophe. Iyakhathaza ukuzama ukufumana efanayo xa zininzi iimpahla ojonga phakathi kwazo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You are being very patient and looking very hard, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name. Well done for trying. I am happy you are helping me."
msgstr "Unomonde kakhulu kwaye uyajongisisa kakhulu,@data.characters.f3_son_4.name Wenze kakuhle ngokuzama.Ndiyavuya uncedisa mna."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"You found two socks with the same pattern! Well done for not giving up, @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! \n"
"\n"
"Because you helped me so well, I now have 5 extra minutes to play with you. What would you like to do?"
msgstr ""
"Ufumene iikawusi ezimbini ezinepateni efanayo! Wenze kakuhle ngokunganikezeli @data.characters.f3_son_4.name! \n"
"\n"
"Ngokuba undinceda kakuhle, ngoku ndinemizuzu emi 5 eyongezelelweyo yokudlala kunye nawe.Ingaba ungathanda ukwenza ntoni?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs reflect on how @data.characters.f3_mother.name praised her son."
msgstr "Khawucinge ngendlela @data.characters.f3_mother.name amncoma ngayo unyana wakhe."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "When @data.characters.f3_mother.name gives @data.characters.f3_son_4.name a hug and extra playtime together, she rewards him and encourages him to stay patient and keep helping with chores."
msgstr "Xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name emwola u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name kwaye enexesha elongezelelekileyo lokudlala kunye, uyamvuza kwaye emkhuthaza ukuba ahlale ngomonde kwaye aqhubeke encedisa kwimisebenzi yasekhaya."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why does @data.characters.f3_mother.name praise her son?"
msgstr "Kutheni u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma unyana wakhe?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To boost confidence"
msgstr "Ukwandisa ukuzithemba"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, he feels good about himself.\n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name uziva kamnandi malunga naye.\n"
"Lonke olukhetho luyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To help him deal with his frustration"
msgstr "Ukumnceda ahlangabezane nonxunguphalo lwakhe"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Exactly! When @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, he will want to keep looking for the socks.\n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Kanye! xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma@data.characters.f3_son_4.name, uya kufuna ukuqhubeka ekhangela iikawusi.\n"
"Lonke olukhetho luyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "To encourage him to want to help more often"
msgstr "Ukumkhuthaza ukuba afune ukunceda rhoqo"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name,
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Exactly! When @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises @data.characters.f3_son_4.name, he will feel good and be more likely to help with chores in the future.\n"
"All of these options are true!"
msgstr ""
"Kanye! xa u@data.characters.f3_mother.name encoma u@data.characters.f3_son_4.name,uya kuziva onwabile kwaye kunokwenzeka ukuba ancedise kwimisebenzi yasekhaya kwixesha elizayo.\n"
"Lonke olukhetho luyinyani!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs see what we can learn from HOW @data.characters.f3_mother.name praises her son."
msgstr "Makhe sibone ukuba yintoni esinokuyifunda KWINDLELA u@data.characters.f3_mother.name ancoma ngayo unyana wakhe."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f3_mother.name‚Äôs
#.      @data.characters.f3_son_4.name‚Äôs
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"@data.characters.f3_mother.name‚Äôs praise works because she: \n"
