#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f3_mother.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Simple and free rewards can help reinforce praise. What rewards does @data.characters.f3_mother.name use?"
msgstr "Imivuzo elula kunye nesimahla inokunceda ukuqinisa ukuncoma.Yeyiphi imivuzo esetyenziswa ngu@data.characters.f3_mother.name?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A hug"
msgstr "Uku mwola"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Extra playtime together"
msgstr "Ixesha lokudlala elongezelelweyo kunye"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That‚Äôs right, giving a simple and free reward helps our children to do behaviours that may be difficult for them."
msgstr "Kulungile! ukunika umvuzo olula nosimahla kunceda abantwana bethu benze izimilo ezinokuba nzima kubo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here are some easy tips for how to use praise."
msgstr "Nazi ezinye indlela ezilula zokusebenzisa ukuncoma."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEE IT"
msgstr "YIBONE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look for good behaviours that you can praise! It can be anything positive or helpful your child does or tries to do."
msgstr "Khangela izimilo ezihle ongakwazi ukuzincoma! Ingayiyo nayiphina elungileyo okanye eluncedo eyenziwa ngumntwana wakhe okanye azama ukuyenza."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Pause and really notice when they are doing something positive. Even if it‚Äôs expected of them.\n"
"\n"
"Praise your child for *trying*. This boosts their self-esteem and confidence, which helps them to learn new behaviours."
msgstr ""
"Yima kwaye uqaphele ngokwenene xa benza into elungileyo. Nokuba ilindelekile kubo.\n"
"\n"
"Mncome umntwana wakho *ngokuzama*. Oku kukhulisa ukuzazi kunye nokuzithemba kwabo, okubanceda bafunde izimilo ezitsha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAY IT"
msgstr "YITHETHE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise them when you see them do something you like. Do this every day ‚Äì even if it‚Äôs something really small."
msgstr "Bancome xa ubabona besenza into oyithandayo. Yenza oku yonke mihla - nokuba yinto encinci ngokwenene."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Tell them specifically what they have done well.\n"
"\n"
"Be enthusiastic and really mean it!\n"
"\n"
"You can show your praise with a big smile and words."
msgstr ""
"Baxelele ngokucacileyo oko bakwenzileyo kakuhle.\n"
"\n"
"Yiba nomdla kwaye uzimisele ngokwenene!\n"
"\n"
"Ungabonisa ukuncoma kwakho ngoncumo olukhulu kunye nangamazwi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REWARD IT"
msgstr "YIVUZE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Give your child a simple, free reward to encourage them to do more of the behaviours that may be difficult for them."
msgstr "Nika umntwana wakho umvuzo olula, wasimahla wokumkhuthaza ukuba enze ngakumbi iizimilo ezinganobu nzima kuye."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Ezinye ingcebiso"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Give your child a hug, extra playtime together, or make their favourite meal. \n"
"\n"
"Simple rewards can be a big motivation for your child to keep trying and show more positive behaviour."
msgstr ""
"Mange umntwana wakho, ixesha elongezelelweyo lokudlala kunye, okanye wenze isidlo asithandayo!\n"
"\n"
"Imivuzo elula ingaba yinkuthazo enkulu kumntwana wakho ukuba aqhubeke ezama kwaye abonise isimilo esilungileyo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Now that you have learned a few tips on how to use praise, let‚Äôs think of specific things we can praise our children for."
msgstr "Ngoku ke sewufundile iingcebiso ezimbalwa zokuba ukusebenzisa njani ukuncoma, makhe sicinge ngezinto ezithile esinokuncoma ngazo abantwana bethu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What is one behaviour your child regularly shows that you can praise them for?"
msgstr "Sesiphi esisimilo sinye umntwana wakho adla ngokusibonisa ongakwazi ukumncoma ngaso?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Cleaning up or helping out"
msgstr "Ukucoca okanye ukuncedisa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Being patient or polite"
msgstr "Ukuba nomonde okanye uhloniphekile"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Trying a new skill"
msgstr "Ukuzama isakhono esitsha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Playing quietly"
msgstr "Edlala ngokuzolileyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Getting ready for school or bed"
msgstr "Ukulungiselela ukuya esikolweni okanye ukulala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, you can praise them for these behaviours‚Ä¶ and many more!"
msgstr "Ewe, usenokwazi ukubancoma ngezi izimilo... kunye nezinye ezininzi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Other"
msgstr "Enye indlela"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Whatever you choose to praise your child for is a great choice. You can praise them whenever they have done something well."
msgstr "Nantoni na okhetha ukuyincoma ngomntwana wakho lukhetho olukhulu olo. Unokumncoma nanini na xa benze into entle."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your home activity is to praise your child for at least 2 things every day.\n"
"Praise yourself too for all your hard work being a parent ‚Äì you deserve it!"
msgstr ""
"Umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya kukuncoma umntwana wakho ngezinto ezi 2 ubuncinane yonke imihla.\n"
"Zincome nawe ngawo wonke umsebenzi wakho onzima wokuba ngumzali-ikufanele lonto!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_2.name's should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how simple praises helped @data.characters.media_female_2.name's family"
msgstr "Cofa udlala ukuze umamele ukuncoma okulula kuncede u@data.characters.media_female_2.name nosapho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When we learned about this praising thing, I thought ‚ÄúWe were never praised for things as children, so why should we start now?‚Äù. But I got interested when I learned what the benefits of praising could be.\n"
"\n"
"Right after learning about praise, I noticed my son doing what he does every day: Packing away his toys after playing. And I said ‚ÄúThank you for packing away your toys, my boy, it really makes me happy that you are helping out to keep the house tidy.‚Äù My son was smiling and he even came to give me a hug, which he never does. \n"
"\n"
"This praising business is hard. I still forget to do it sometimes. But praising really makes a difference. I never thought that a simple praise could make such a change in a person!"
msgstr ""
"Xa besifunda malunga ngalento yokuncoma, ndicinga ukuba, \"Zange sanconywa ngezinto njengabantwana, ngoko kutheni kufuneka siqalise ngoku?\" Kodwa ndaba nomdla xa ndafunda ngeemivuzo yokuncoma ingayintoni.\n"
"\n"
"Kanye emva kokuba ndifundile ngokuncoma, ndiyabona unyana wam esenza le nto ayenzayo yonke imihla: Ukuqoqosha izinto zakhe zokudlala emva kokudlala. Ndaye ndathi \"Enkosi ngokuqoqosha izinto zakho zokudlala mfana wam, iyandonwabisa ngokwenene into yokuba uyancedisa ukugcina indlu icocekile. \"Unyana wam ebencumile kwaye wade wafika wandiwola, into angazange ayenze. \n"
"\n"
"Lomsebenzi wokuncoma unzima. Ndisalibala ukuyenza ngamanye amaxesha. Kodwa ukuncoma kuyawenza umahluko ngokwenene. Zange ndiyicinge into yokuncoma nje inokwenza utshintsho emntwini!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you praise your child today?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi ukuncoma umntwana wakho namhlanje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Parents who practise praise at home get better results!"
msgstr "Kuhle kakhulu! Abazali abaziqhelanisa nokuncoma ekhaya bafumana iziphumo ezingcono!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try praising your child for something simple at first, like putting away their toy. Praise is a powerful parenting skill!"
msgstr "Ungayenza lonto! Zama ukuncoma umntwana wakho ngento elula ekuqaleni, njengokubeke into yakhe yokudlala. Ukuncoma sisakhono esinamandla kakhulu sobuzali!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. With time, giving praise will become easier. Try to praise yourself for something first, like _\"Well done for using @global.app_name. It shows you care.\"_"
msgstr "Kulungile. Exesheni, ukuncoma kuzakuya kubalula. Zama ukuzincoma wena ngento kuqala, njengo_ \"Umsebenzi omhle ngokusebenzisa @global.app_name. Ibonakalisa ukuba uyakhathala.\"_"

